Use `cc.loader.load` for batch loading and `cc.loader.loadJson` for JSON:

```typescript
// Load multiple resources
cc.loader.load(['res/hero.png', 'res/level1.json'], (err) => {
    if (err) {
        cc.error('Load failed:', err);
        return;
    }
    // Resources are cached, access via getRes
    const levelData = cc.loader.getRes('res/level1.json');
    startGame(levelData);
});

// Load JSON specifically
