    const uiPos = cc.director.convertToUI(gamePos);
    element.style.left = uiPos.x + 'px';
    element.style.top = uiPos.y + 'px';
}
```

Note: In Cocos2d-x, game logic typically uses GL coordinates. UI coordinates are mainly needed when interfacing with browser DOM elements or platform-specific UI.

